Developer Terms of Use
des:
Duckfeet apply a minimalist, foot-shaped form that offers ample room for toes to splay naturally. Midsoles and uppers are constructed with vegetable-tanned leather, and some models feature a shearling wool lining. Subtle variations in the leather reveal unique stories and character with wear. The outsoles are made from all-natural, shock-absorbent crepe rubber and can be resoled. Each pair of Duckfeet is produced in Europe without synthetic materials. Exclusive-quality Terracare leather employs environmentally friendly and sustainable processes all other components originate in the European Union. Duckfeet USA proudly brings the Duckfeet brand to the United States. 

You can start this skill by saying
"Alexa, open duck feet"
followed by
- find me sandals
- what is the return policy
